{"tid":2428004,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"記住要共熱血公民分享每個夜晚","createTime":"2021-03-01T08:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T11:09:26.000Z","uid":38189,"like":30,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb258631ccfa1c51102a02773a8d7c0de4f4564","tid":2428004,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:42:11.000Z","msg":"記住要共熱血公民分享每個夜晚<br />\n別忘掉皇上靠堅持醫好每個傷患<br />\n既是有力五區都贏即管好好作反<br />\n無懼國安打倒建制<br />\n<br />\n無用泛民來勸告　一街深黃言滔滔<br />\n不需坐下來計數　前行吧　你想做　全意做<br />\n(想做就做 票投十號)<br />\n如沒有無窮氣數　也可跟陳雲賭一鋪<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在&nbsp;※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt13WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=e11591af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網<br />\n這段少年時間　有誰無悔　熱血青春要消耗 <br />\n<br />\n記住要訂熱血早晨朝朝看到夜晚<br />\n別忘掉洋達靠堅持天天對抗港共<br />\n記住趁尚有些金錢捐多一些課金<br />\n如若你還淘氣　你還強壯　盡管支撐別退款<br />\n<br />\n記住要共熱血公民歡呼至到達旦<br />\n別忘掉皇上靠堅持擺多兩個街站<br />\n掛念昨日四眼通渠即管好好作反<br />\n重奪五區修改憲法　皇上燦爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55e2e1603f489d7750a973a58214805b5c004b5","tid":2428004,"uid":18868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7abdbc97146d7bddb7f46cdfc50dd92251570e","tid":2428004,"uid":234509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:42:44.000Z","msg":"作唔作睡港父"},{"pid":"934f5e903dacad464b969a0ce6eb37d3fa98a86a","tid":2428004,"uid":73381,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"共熱血公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拉！"},{"pid":"17dce46939f24d5cd0b6c3ea12b230e8fc5aa262","tid":2428004,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b7abdbc97146d7bddb7f46cdfc50dd92251570e","tid":2428004,"uid":234509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"c